description: Welcome to the Rocket wiki! Rocket is an extensible Unturned 3 Server Mod. It acts as a simple wrapper around the games core functionality and loads custom commands, configurations and gameobjects. With a built in permission system and growing plugin ecosystem its the best way for server admins to customize their Unturned 3 server to their needs.
releaseNotes: If you want do download the latest Rocket, head over to our website at https://rocket.foundation/get-rocket/. You can also browse the official plugin repository.
